replies.body:
I know a lot of people like it, so I don't wish for it to be removed, but I really don't like the map. The only way people who aren't very skilled rushers can get the monuments are to tunnel underground, skybridge, or just get really lucky.. 
Honestly, mid-field is pretty fun, but the game lasts forever if there are good midfielders because no one can get pass unless they tunnel or make a skybridge.
I agree with you, but lots of people have fun on this map; you might want to reconsider
wanting it removed. 
Talking avout Luar xD
